Intelligent Processing

Developing for tomorrow, delivering today

  • Intelligently streamlining

    Use our integrated software solutions for accounts, tax and audit to simplify and streamline the production of your final accounts and corporation tax returns.

  • Intelligently collaborating

    Collaborate remotely with staff and clients on real-time data and increase your efficiency and connectivity with our cloud based solutions.

  • Intelligently analysing

    Increase value to your clients quickly and efficiently by interrogating, verifying and reviewing data to find anomalies and identify risks.

Simplify and streamline 

Whether you work in practice or business, our software can help save you time and money, giving you more freedom to focus on other projects. Established for over 30 years, we work with a large proportion of the Top 100 practices as well as a multitude of mid-tier and sole practitioners. Our software is also widely used throughout the business sector for the preparation of final accounts and tax filings. 

Designed by accountants for accountants, all our products promote a completely paperless environment, enabling accountants and auditors around the world to collaborate on screen. Our products significantly reduce the time involved in all manner of accountancy processes, enabling auditors and finance teams to focus their skills and expertise elsewhere.
